[20.322352, "o", "============================================================\r\nTASK\r\n============================================================\r\nExtract the following fields from this invoice snippet:\r\n    vendor, amount, currency, due_date, invoice_number\r\n\r\n    Invoice snippet:\r\n    INVOICE #INV-2024-0892\r\n    From: Acme Software Ltd\r\n    Amount Due: $4,250.00 USD\r\n    Payment Due: March 15, 2025\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\nFOSSIL SEARCH — checking for similar past failures\r\n============================================================\r\n"]
[21.061624, "o", "[FOSSIL: Similar past failures retrieved]\r\n\r\n--- Fossil 1 (similarity: 0.48) ---\r\nSituation: agent asked to extract a JSON object from a markdown code block returned by an LLM\r\nWhat failed: json.loads() failed because the string included ```json and ``` fences — the model wrapped the output in markdown even though raw JSON was requested\r\nHow it was resolved: strip markdown fences before parsing: re.sub(r'^```[a-z]*\r\n|```$', '', text.strip())\r\n\r\n[End of FOSSIL context]\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\nAGENT RUNNING — llama-3.3-70b-versatile\r\n============================================================\r\n"]
[21.635378, "o", "Raw output:\r\n{\r\n\"vendor\": \"Acme Software Ltd\",\r\n\"amount\": \"4250.00\",\r\n\"currency\": \"USD\",\r\n\"due_date\": \"March 15, 2025\",\r\n\"invoice_number\": \"INV-2024-0892\"\r\n}\r\n\r\n"]
